{"lemma":"رُقْعاتٌ","slug":"رُقْعاتٌ","root":"ر.ق.ع","root_slug":"ر-ق-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ق-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16370","n16375","n16376"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%82%D9%92%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"patch, piece of cloth for mending"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"area, spot, patch of land"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ticket, label, billet"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ruq.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16370","headword_ar":"رَقَعَهُ","root":"rqE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqoEN","text_ar":"رَقْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He patched it; pieced it; put a piece of cloth in the place thereof that was cut"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repaired it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and closed up the hole"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"holes thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a patch"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"patches;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) namely, a garment, or piece of cloth; (S, Msb, K;) and in like manner, a skin, or hide; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rq~Ehu","text_ar":"رقّعهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taroqiyEN","text_ar":"تَرْقِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trqyE","text_ar":"ترقيع"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"patching"},{"kind":"text","text":"a garment, or piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in several places."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stopped it up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"closed it up;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, any hole, or aperture; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rq~Ehu","text_ar":"رقّعهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in the saying of 'Omar Ibn-Abee-Rabee'ah,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wakun~a A_i*aA A^aboSaronaniY A^awosamiEonaniY\n                      \n                     \n                        xarajona faraq~aEona AlkuwaY biAlmaHaAjiri"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they"},{"kind":"text","text":"(referring to women)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used, when they"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1137},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saw me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heard me, to come forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarajona","text_ar":"خَرَجْنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being used for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxorujona","text_ar":"يَخْرُجْنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and close up the apertures in the walls with the eyes and the parts immediately around them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repaired it"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a figurative sense; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rq~Ehu","text_ar":"رقّعهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaroqaEu diynahu bitawobatihi","text_ar":"يَرْقَعُ دِينَهُ بِتَوْبَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repairs his religion by his repentance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rq~E","text_ar":"رقّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dunoyaAhu baA=xiratihi","text_ar":"دُنْيَاهُ بَا=خِرَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repaired his state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, in the present word by"},{"kind":"text","text":"sacrificing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his blessings in the world to come"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: whence the saying of 'AbdAllah Ibn-El-Mubárak,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"nuraq~iEu dunoyaAnaA bitamoziyqi diyninaA\n                      \n                     \n                        falaAd diynunaA yaboqaY walaA maA nuraq~iEu"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We repair our state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, in the present world by the rending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marring, of our religion, so that neither our religion remains nor what we repair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAlahu wamaEiy$atahu","text_ar":"حَالَهُ وَمَعِيشَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rq~E","text_ar":"رقّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repaired, amended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put to rights, his state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, and his means of subsistence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSolaHa","text_ar":"اَصْلَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~aHa","text_ar":"رَقَّحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, * TA:) with which latter ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rq~E","text_ar":"رقّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also syn. as signifying (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he gained, acquired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"property; accord. to an explanation of its inf. n.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trqyE","text_ar":"ترقيع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSilu","text_ar":"يَصِلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkalaAma fayaroqaEu baEoDahu bibaEoDK","text_ar":"الكَلَامَ فَيَرْقَعُ بَعْضَهُ بِبَعْضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He connects the language, and repairs one part thereof by inserting another"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: said of a poet. (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taroqiyEN","text_ar":"تَرْقِيعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)  [The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interpolating:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adding to a tradition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrative."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA raqaEa maroqaEFA","text_ar":"مَا رَقَعَ مَرْقَعًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not patch a place of patching,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place to be patched;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrought not, anything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna muEaAwiyapu yaloqamu biyadK wayaroqaEu","text_ar":"كَانَ مُعَاوِيَةُ يَلْقَمُ بِيَدٍ وَيَرْقَعُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^uxoraY","text_ar":"بِاُخْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mo'áwiyeh used to put morsels into his mouth with one hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and spread another"},{"kind":"text","text":"hand"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that the portions of his morsels that fell might become scattered upon it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, Sgh, K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEa Alr~akiy~apa","text_ar":"رَقَعَ الرَّكِيَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-' Abbád, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEahaA biAlr~iqaAEi","text_ar":"رَقَعَهَا بِالرِّقَاعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqoEN","text_ar":"رَقْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cased, the interior of the well for the space of the stature of a man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twice that measure, fearing its becoming demolished,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its upper part."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEa xal~apa AlfaArisi","text_ar":"رَقَعَ خَلَّةَ الفَارِسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He closed up the interval between him and the horseman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he reached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overtook, the horseman, and pierced him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thrust him;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxal~apu","text_ar":"الخَلَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying the interval, or intervening space, between the piercer, or thruster, and the pierced, or thrust. (O, K, TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEa AlgaraDa bisahomK","text_ar":"رَقَعَ الغَرَضَ بِسَهْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aqoEapa","text_ar":"الرَّقْعَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"struck, the butt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"target, with an arrow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqoEu ruqoEapK","text_ar":"رَقْعُ رُقْعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)  Any"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hitting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"striking."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEa","text_ar":"رَقَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in any manner; with a whip; and otherwise; as in the phrases"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEahu kaf~FA","text_ar":"رَقَعَهُ كَفًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck him a slap with the hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yaroqaEu AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"هُوَ يَرْقَعُ الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"birijolihi","text_ar":"بِرِجْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beats the ground with his foot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEa Al$~ayoxu","text_ar":"رَقَعَ الشَّيْخُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The old man supported himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bore, upon his two palms,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he struck the ground with the palms of his hands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order to rise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b9-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEahu","text_ar":"رَقَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEahu bqawolihi","text_ar":"رَقَعَهُ بقَوْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He censured him, reviled him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"satirized him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raquEa","text_ar":"رَقُعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaAEapN","text_ar":"رَقَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, stupid, foolish, deficient in sense;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shattered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marred, in his intellect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyE","text_ar":"رَقِيع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n16375","headword_ar":"رَقْعَةٌ","root":"rqE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound of the arrow in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon, the butt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"target."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n16376","headword_ar":"رُقْعَةٌ","root":"rqE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A patch;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rag, with which a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, is patched,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repaired:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riqaAEN","text_ar":"رِقَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqaEN","text_ar":"رُقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~aAHibu kaAlr~uqoEapi fiY Alv~awobi faA@Tolubohu mu$aAkilFA","text_ar":"الصَّاحِبُ كَالرُّقْعَةِ فِى الثَّوْبِ فَا@طْلُبْهُ مُشَاكِلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The companion is like the patch in the garment; therefore seek thou the one that is suitable"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"patch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of mange, or scab: (TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commencement"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the mange, or scab: (K, TA: [in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHarob","text_ar":"الحَرْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljarab","text_ar":"الجَرَب"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riqaAEN","text_ar":"رِقَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"of land, or ground,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjoining another piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is in some manner distinguished therefrom;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a patch"},{"kind":"text","text":"of land, or ground: and in like manner, of herbage]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riqaAEN","text_ar":"رِقَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riqaAEu AlA^aroDi muxotalifapN","text_ar":"رِقَاعُ الاَرْضِ مُخْتَلِفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The patches of the land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground, are various,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diverse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi ruqoEapN mina AlkalaA^i","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ رُقْعَةٌ مِنَ الكَلَاِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is a patch of herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA wajadonaA gayora riqaAEK mino","text_ar":"مَا وَجَدْنَا غَيْرَ رِقَاعٍ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$obK","text_ar":"عُشْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We found not"},{"kind":"text","text":"aught"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save patches of green herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b5-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A note, billet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"short letter:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a short written petition"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"memorial, addressed to a prince or governor: a ticket: a label:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain thing that is written:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riqaAEN","text_ar":"رِقَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) [and accord. to modern usage"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqaEN","text_ar":"رُقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also]. Hence the saying in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajiYo'u A^aHadukumo yawoma AlqiyaAmapi EalaY raqabatihi riqaAEN taxofiqu","text_ar":"يَجِىْءُ اَحَدُكُمْ يَوْمَ القِيَامَةِ عَلَى رَقَبَتِهِ رِقَاعٌ تَخْفِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One of you will come, on the day of resurrection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"having, suspended"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon his neck, billets fluttering"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning, by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rqAE","text_ar":"رقاع"},{"kind":"text","text":", the claims to be made upon him, or the dues incumbent on him, written on the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rqAE","text_ar":"رقاع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A butt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"target, at which to shoot;"},{"kind":"text","text":"also termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqoEapu garaDK","text_ar":"رُقْعَةُ غَرَضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A chess-table;"},{"kind":"text","text":"also termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqoEapu Al$~iToranoji","text_ar":"رُقْعَةُ الشِّطْرَنْجِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so called because it is patched [with squares]. (T A.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"original matter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) of a garment, or piece of cloth; (S, TA;) or of a thing: (TA:) or (tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thickness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a garment, or piece of cloth. (Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqoEapu h`*aA Alv~awobi jay~idapN","text_ar":"رُقْعَةُ هٰذَا الثَّوْبِ جَيِّدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substance"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thickness of this garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, is good."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b9-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riqaAEN","text_ar":"رِقَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"casing, which is constructed in the upper part of the interior of a well when one fears its becoming demolished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaEa Alr~ikiy~apa","text_ar":"رَقَعَ الرِّكِيَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Mgh","TA"]}]}}